trans-unit.source: Contains a strongly typed collection of <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation"></xref> objects.
Initializes an instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolationCollection"></xref> class.
Checks whether the collection contains the specified <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation"></xref> object.
The <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation"></xref> object to locate in the collection.
`true` if the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation"></xref> object exists in the collection; otherwise `false`.
Copies the elements from the collection to an array, starting at a specified index of the array.
An array of type <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation"></xref> to which to copy the contents of the collection.
The zero-based index in array at which copying begins.
Returns the zero-based index of a specified <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation"></xref> in the collection.
The <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation"></xref> to find in the collection.
The zero-based index of the specified <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation"></xref>, or -1 if the element was not found in the collection.
Inserts a <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation"></xref> to the collection at the specified location.
The zero-based index in the collection at which to insert the violation.
The <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation"></xref> to insert.
Gets or sets the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation"></xref> element at a specified index in the collection.
The zero-based index in the collection.
A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation"></xref> object that exists at the specified index.
Removes a specified <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation"></xref> from the collection.
The <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation"></xref> to remove from the collection.
Returns a <xref href="System.String"></xref> representation of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation"></xref> objects in the collection.
A <xref href="System.String"></xref> representation of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation"></xref> objects in the collection.
Returns an enumerator that iterates through a collection of <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.BasicProfileViolation"></xref> objects.
An <xref href="System.Collections.IEnumerator"></xref> object that can be used to iterate through the collection.
